{"tid":2261783,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"新加坡停用南韓流感疫苗","createTime":"2020-10-28T14:45:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-28T14:50:56.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"ea801401bb27bdd271c2ff0ae2c604f23e57ac3a","tid":2261783,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T14:45:12.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20201027/SPN73RRL7FALHGMBRVHQI35RLQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20201027%2FSPN73RRL7FALHGMBRVHQI35RLQ%2F&d=wqADD7%2BrbugmZDmBsEVo7AomF%2BlBZ%2FxAFwVMru4Rc7Q%3D&h=d7eac019\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20201027%2FSPN73RRL7FALHGMBRVHQI35RLQ%2F&h=8eb67be0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20201027/SPN73RRL7FALHGMBRVHQI35RLQ/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n新加坡停用南韓流感疫苗<br />\n<br />\n南韓本月實施全國免費流感疫苗接種計劃以來，至少有59人注射疫苗後死亡，雖然韓方一再強調兩者無直接關聯，但新加坡決定暫停使用涉事的兩款疫苗，以策安全。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n南韓現多宗死亡個案<br />\n<br />\n新加坡前晚宣佈暫停使用南韓SK生物科學公司（SK Bioscience）生產的SKYCellflu四價流感疫苗及法國賽諾菲（Sanofi）生產的VaxigripTetra疫苗，但獅城強調，措施只是以防萬一，當地並無收到有人接種後死亡的報告，當局會繼續向韓方了解情況。<br />\n<br />\n南韓為了防止即將來臨的冬季或出現武漢肺炎和流感「雙重大流行」，。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n南韓衞生部門試圖平息公眾的疑慮，。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n路透社<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/s7unrMqWvCK1arTy64_0Bc3wnmQ=/1519x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/ABK6PGXZ7FA43J6K6MAOF563DA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fs7unrMqWvCK1arTy64_0Bc3wnmQ%3D%2F1519x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FABK6PGXZ7FA43J6K6MAOF563DA.jpg&h=ff1a7c6c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■南韓使用的賽諾菲生產的VaxigripTetra疫苗，被新加坡停用。"},{"pid":"b8d129054911fffd03272b72b65fc3a0cb83c279","tid":2261783,"uid":143499,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T14:50:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}